{"tid":1653481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Now新聞台車長身上至少9處明顯傷痕","createTime":"2019-10-14T05:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T10:08:38.000Z","uid":53379,"like":197,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"acc11dc738c2134586aded388653aaa79fff7307","tid":1653481,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:52:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Now新聞台車長身上至少9處明顯傷痕</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nNow新聞台一名車長凌晨在旺角警署外，前往取採訪車途中，後腦位置懷疑中布袋彈受傷，其後被多名防暴警察押入警署。Now新聞台引述車長稱，在警署內遭暴力對待，身上最少有9處明顯傷痕，包括額頭、兩邊手肘、手掌。至於右邊面下顎骨裂，要留院接受手術，部分傷勢是在警署內做成。<br />\n<br />\nNow新聞台又引述車長說，當時有數名警員將他帶往樓梯，有人將他的面按在牆上，又用警棍打他的頭、手及腳，期間他已多次向警員表明為Now新聞台員工。Now新聞台表示，受傷車長為外判司機，當時手持印有公司標記的反光背心。<br />\n<br />\n事發凌晨一時許，Now新聞台說，車長中彈倒地的位置，距離泊於旺角警署外的採訪車約幾十米。該台攝影師當時曾上前表明為同事，但被多名防暴警員驅趕。車長被扣留兩個多小時後，警方確認他有合理原因在現場，將他釋放，再由救護車送往廣華醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486054-20191014.htm?fbclid=IwAR3-tbuROzmIbKC7eNawsor7H4bAUNkzvg9m2AjOwYlo1DGgDcctJHg8Tv8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486054-20191014.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3-tbuROzmIbKC7eNawsor7H4bAUNkzvg9m2AjOwYlo1DGgDcctJHg8Tv8&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=b4fba37c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486054-20191014.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3-tbuROzmIbKC7eNawsor7H4bAUNkzvg9m2AjOwYlo1DGgDcctJHg8Tv8&h=cda948d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486054-20191014.htm?fbclid=IwAR3-tbuROzmIbKC7eNawsor7H4bAUNkzvg9m2AjOwYlo1DGgDcctJHg8Tv8</a>"},{"pid":"e6ceebac93590d0603f621482943b421926eb795","tid":1653481,"uid":209543,"like":8,"dislike":19,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:53:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3143ec15581cf460380525cc8b6b2031de989e1d","tid":1653481,"uid":21887,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:54:18.000Z","msg":"支持Now追究到底"},{"pid":"a