,"msg":"記者都打到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78e29da96f0daf2205245d071dc4357e8cedbebd","tid":1653481,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:41:56.000Z","msg":"黑警而家呢個精神狀態 應該係上層洗佢地腦 你地已經洗濕左隻腳 盲算而家收手都會追究到 一係你就同我繼續打 越打越多"},{"pid":"1b59fe6f58f5867bcdfa2e488169874bb4506434","tid":1653481,"uid":256783,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:43:11.000Z","msg":"其實個重點係<br />\n<br />\nNOW , 其實喺抗爭者眼中既評級係 「中性」, 無話偏幫邊一面<br />\n<br />\n班狗賊以為啲傳媒全部都係偏幫抗爭者<br />\n所以就毆打佢<br />\n<br />\n事件帶出既結論<br />\n班狗賊 4 個月嚟玻璃心碎哂<br />\n唔肯正視係狗賊做野有問題<br />\n一味怪哂市民, 記者<br />\n<br />\n場運動拖長嚟打既話, 抗爭一方勝算好大<br />\n因為班狗賊既精神會率先捱唔住, 輕則有情緒病 , 重則痴線 + 有谷到有惡疾"},{"pid":"9122ac41dc8604373907eda4406a0cb4c9c9df76","tid":1653481,"uid":72991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71618cdb16bd6c0155dc8963127392e17891466d","tid":1653481,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:46:36.000Z","msg":"你老母仆街死狗"},{"pid":"5c9e9518329fe6b2846a627524052a086208249d","tid":1653481,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acc11dc738c2134586aded388653aaa79fff7307","tid":1653481,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:52:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Now新聞台車長身上至少9處明顯傷痕</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nNow新聞台一名車長凌晨在旺角警署外，前往取採訪車途中，後腦位置懷疑中布袋彈受傷，其後被多名防暴警察押入警署。Now新聞台引述車長稱，在警署內遭暴力對待，身上最少有9處明顯傷痕，包括額頭、兩邊手肘、手掌。至於右邊面下顎骨裂，要留院接受手術，部分傷勢是在警署內做成。<br />\n<br />\nNow新聞台又引述車長說，當時有數名警員將他帶往樓梯，有人將他的面按在牆上，又用警棍打他的頭、手及腳，期間他已多次向警員表明為Now新聞台員工。Now新聞台表示，受傷車長為外判司機，當時手持印有公司標記的反光背心。<br />\n<br />\n事發凌晨一時許，Now新聞台說，車長中彈倒地的位置，距離泊於旺角警署外的採訪車約幾十米。該台攝影師當時曾上前表明為同事，但被多名防暴警員驅趕。車長被扣留兩個多小時後，警方確認他有合理原因在現場，將他釋放，再由救護車送往廣華醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486054-20191014.htm?fbclid=IwAR3-tbuROzmIbKC7eNawsor7H4bAUNkzvg9m2AjOwYlo1DGgDcctJHg8Tv8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486054-20191014.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3-tbuROzmIbKC7eNawsor7H4bAUNkzvg9m2AjOwYlo1DGgDcctJHg8Tv8&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=b4fba37c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486054-20191014.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3-tbuROzmIbKC7eNawsor7H4bAUNkzvg9m2AjOwYlo1DGgDcctJHg8Tv8&h=cda948d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486054-20191014.htm?fbclid=IwAR3-tbuROzmIbKC7eNawsor7H4bAUNkzvg9m2AjOwYlo1DGgDcctJHg8Tv8</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:46:54.000Z","msg":"車長如果肯出相會更大回響"},{"pid":"3e0aa736c690671e52b3cee37813ddc625835c16","tid":1653481,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:47:20.000Z","msg":"班狗傻撚曬癲撚曬"},{"pid":"efc28668c712465191fa9407f5fab9be406f2e77","tid":1653481,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:48:06.000Z","msg":"澤仔仲唔做野"},{"pid":"475a9670db11620c234b9c86e22ba4f04ef3761f","tid":1653481,"uid":272119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"083a925a9637b433d7fc4e971735e6185fda9717","tid":1653481,"uid":96871,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:56:05.000Z","msg":"呢單爆呀 記者都比人打到咁撚樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:48:29.000Z","msg":"路過既街坊唔知會點"},{"pid":"344ffa96180acdf468638898ff9c45d112d94c68","tid":1653481,"uid":58160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:49:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68f5123b0bb50dd299f556545bd38b1bf583c546","tid":1653481,"uid":255744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:49:53.000Z","msg":"嚟緊狗記又班記者又jer住追問啦"},{"pid":"f69122eb5faf6f5840c82bdffffed427afab6bd5","tid":1653481,"uid":259860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:50:02.000Z","msg":"<i